"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:4.2.4\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.2.4</span> 标题：香坛（incense altar）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִזְבֵּחַ, מִקְטָר, קְטֹרֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mizbeach (miqtar qetoreth))</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:1\">EXO 30:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:27\">EXO 30:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:8\">EXO 31:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:15\">EXO 35:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:25\">EXO 37:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:38\">EXO 39:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:5\">EXO 40:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:26\">EXO 40:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev4:7\">LEV 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:11\">NUM 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:20\">1KI 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:22\">1KI 6:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:48\">1KI 7:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr6:34\">1CH 6:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:18\">1CH 28:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:19\">2CH 4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:16\">2CH 26:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:19\">2CH 26:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:22\">EZK 41:22</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מְקַטֶּרֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：meqatereth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:14\">2CH 30:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：לְבֵנָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：lvenah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:3\">ISA 65:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：שֻׁלְחָן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：shulchan)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:22\">EZK 41:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:16\">EZK 44:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：θυμιατήριον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：thumiatērion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:4\">HEB 9:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：θυσιαστήριον, θυμίαμα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：thusiastērion (tou thumiamatos), thumiama)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:11\">LUK 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:9\">REV 6:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:3\">REV 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:3\">REV 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:3\">REV 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:5\">REV 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:13\">REV 9:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:18\">REV 14:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:7\">REV 16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:21\">1MA 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc4:49\">1MA 4:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc4:50\">1MA 4:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc2:5\">2MA 2:5</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0447_incense_altar.jpg\" alt=\"香坛\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">香坛 (© Ori229, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>香坛是一个木制的桌柜，全部用锤出来的金子包着。香坛比祭坛小，高约1米（40英寸），每边长50厘米（20英寸）。根据<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:10\">EXO 30:10</a> 的描述，这个坛也有“翘角”（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.2.1.1 祭坛的翘角 (horns of the altar)&lt;REALIA:4.2.1.1&gt;</a> ）。香坛放在帐幕和耶路撒冷圣殿的圣所内，祭司每日在香坛上烧香（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.4.7.1 香、乳香 (incense, frankincense)&lt;REALIA:4.4.7.1&gt;</a> ）和祈祷。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/PTZ-0080_high_priest_incense_altar.jpg\" alt=\"大祭司在圣殿中的香坛前\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">大祭司在圣殿中的香坛前 (© Ray Pritz by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>在有些语言中，“香坛”可译作“焚香敬拜上帝的地方”。翻译者必须避免译文暗示坛是用香做成的。另外也可以译作：“百姓焚香献给上帝的桌子／地方／火盆／灶台”，或“百姓焚烧膏油并且上帝以之为馨香的桌子／地方／火盆／灶台”。</p>\n<p>如果目标语言文化中有任何用于仪式的类似桌子或炭炉，那么这可能是一个合适的译词。</p>\n<p>香坛和祭司的香炉（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.4.7 香炉 (censer)&lt;REALIA:4.4.7&gt;</a> ）之间的关系可能会让人迷惑不解。努德西伊（Noordtzij，第144页）的注解会有助于我们了解：“因为这里（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:6\">NUM 16:6</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:17\">NUM 16:17</a> ）的香炉用于烧香，有些学者推断作者不明白<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:1-Exod30:10\">EXO 30:1–EXO 30:10</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:25-Exod37:29\">EXO 37:25–EXO 37:29</a> 所记的金香坛，但这是基于一个误解。香坛供每日烧香之用，香的烟雾可以说是隔开了圣所和至圣所，这样，供职的祭司就不致因为接近临在约柜上面的上帝而有危险。但是，香炉只有在祭司（在以色列只有大祭司）靠近约柜时才用到（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:12\">LEV 16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:13\">LEV 16:13</a> ）”。另参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.4.5 小铲子、火盆 (small shovel, firepan)&lt;REALIA:4.4.5&gt;</a> 中的注解。</p>\n<p>把杠穿过香坛两侧的环，就可以将其抬起来（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:4\">EXO 30:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:5\">EXO 30:5</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:27\">EXO 37:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:28\">EXO 37:28</a> ）。参上文<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.1 约柜 (Covenant Box, Ark of the Covenant)&lt;REALIA:4.1&gt;</a> 的讨论。与抬约柜的杠不同，抬香坛等物的杠在物件安放在指定位置后要抽出来。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:3\">ISA 65:3</a> ：字面意为“他们在砖上烧香”这个分句的确切意思不详，然而先知显然是在谴责以色列人随从某种异教习俗。翻译者可以参照<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Spanish Common Language Version (Dios Habla Hoy)\">SPCL</abbr> ，将“砖”译为“砖筑的坛”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 类似）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 非常明确地译为“异教的祭坛”（“pagan altars”）。先知预言的重点是：以色列人在圣殿香坛以外的地点烧香，这是上帝所禁止的。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:9\">REV 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:3\">REV 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:5\">REV 8:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:13\">REV 9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:1\">REV 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:18\">REV 14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:7\">REV 16:7</a> ：《启示录》八次提到坛，但是对于约翰每次说的是不是同一个坛，以及在每节经文中他指的是哪种坛，解经家意见不一。芒思（Mounce，第157页）对<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:9\">REV 6:9</a> 的注解饶有意味：“猜测坛是祭坛还是香坛可能并不重要。献祭的主题暗示前者，而上升的祷告（第10节）似乎暗示后者。在约翰的异象中，这两者没有理由不合在一起。”但是，如果翻译者找不到一个涵盖这两种坛的统称来保留《启示录》经文的模糊性，那么这种区分就很重要了。如果翻译者必须在“祭坛”（焚烧祭牲的坛）和“香坛”（用来烧香的坛）之间做出选择，那么基本上有两种做法：（1）从两个词中选定一个，并在全书中统一使用这个词；（2）根据上下文来选择用词。</p>\n<p>在《启示录》中，提到坛的第一处经文是<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:9\">REV 6:9</a> ；经文似乎表明这种坛及其位置已经众所周知，或者作者预设读者知道这是在类似圣殿的背景中。这种参照应予以保留，即使译本的读者可能对此还不熟悉。翻译者选用的词语应清楚表明，这种坛是献给上帝的。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
